name: Subterror Disruption
effect:
When this card is activated: You can Special Summon 1 "Subterror" monster from your Deck in face-down Defense Position.
Once per turn, if a monster(s) is Normal or Special Summoned: You can activate 1 of these effects;
● Change 1 face-down "Subterror" monster you control to face-up Attack or Defense Position.
● Change 1 face-up "Subterror" monster you control to face-down Defense Position.
You can only activate 1 "Subterror Disruption" per turn.
